# Thakar Kitchen
> Authentic Indian ready-to-eat food brand based in Morbi, Gujarat, India. All products are 100% natural, made with groundnut oil, no preservatives, no added colours, and are FSSAI certified.
## About
Thakar Kitchen makes traditional Gujarati and North Indian ready-to-eat meals using Retort Technology — the same sterilisation process used for astronaut and army food. Meals are fully cooked, sealed, and shelf-stable for 12 months without any preservatives. No refrigeration needed. Heat and eat in 3–5 minutes.
