## FAQ
- Q: Do I need to refrigerate it? A: No. Store in a cool dry place. Refrigerate only after opening.
- Q: Is it safe for kids and elderly? A: Yes. No preservatives, no artificial colours, 100% natural ingredients.
- Q: How long does it last? A: 12 months from manufacture date, unopened.
- Q: Can I carry it on flights? A: Yes. Travel friendly, no liquid restrictions apply to sealed retort pouches.
- Q: What is Retort Technology? A: High heat and pressure sterilisation that kills all bacteria naturally — no preservatives needed.
